{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·002.1", "text_original": "牆有茨，不可埽也，中冓之言，不可道也，所可道也，言之醜也。", "text_normalized": "牆有茨，不可埽也，中冓之言，不可道也，所可道也，言之醜也。", "notes": "牆有茨 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·002.2", "text_original": "牆有茨，不可襄也，中冓之言，不可詳也，所可詳也，言之長也。", "text_normalized": "牆有茨，不可襄也，中冓之言，不可詳也，所可詳也，言之長也。", "notes": "牆有茨 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·002.3", "text_original": "牆有茨，不可束也，中冓之言，不可讀也，所可讀也，言之辱也。", "text_normalized": "牆有茨，不可束也，中冓之言，不可讀也，所可讀也，言之辱也。", "notes": "牆有茨 Chinese stanza 3."}
